comments.body: Can we put these fake stub classes into one file like: `SparkYarnTestHelper` or something else? That will possibly reduce the file number. Both for here `StubApplicationAttemptId` and `StubApplicationId`. If nowhere else use these classes, we could even put these classes into `ExtensionServiceIntegrationSuite.scala`. Just my thought :).
I'm using them more in the tests in the later patches. I can (and will) move them into the test helper, but be assured, there's a lot more tests to come.
nit: nuke the extra empty lines.
